OL,3,CNinja sword ban under Ronan's Law set
OL,4,Cto come into force by summer
OL,6,FA ban on ninja swords, campaigned for
OL,7,Fby the family of murdered
OL,8,FWolverhampton teenager Ronan Kanda, is
OL,9,Fset to come into force by summer.
OL,11,FThe 16-year-old was stabbed to death
OL,12,Fin a case of mistaken identity, yards
OL,13,Faway from his home on Mount Road in
OL,14,FLanesfield in June 2022.
OL,16,FPrabjeet Veadhesa and Sukhman
OL,17,FShergill, both 17, were sentenced to
OL,18,Flife in prison, with a minimum of 18
OL,19,Fyears, for Ronan's murder.
