OL,3,CNinja sword ban under Ronan's Law set
OL,4,Cto come into force by summer
OL,6,FHis mother, Pooja Kanda, has
OL,7,Fcampaigned for a law change to ban the
OL,8,Fdangerous weapons.
OL,10,FThe move to ban the blades will be
OL,11,Flaid before Parliament on Thursday and
OL,12,Fwill come into force in the summer
OL,13,Fonce it has gained approval in
OL,14,FParliament.
OL,16,FIt means it will be illegal to
OL,17,Fpossess, sell, make or import the
OL,18,Fweapon from August 1 as the final part
OL,19,Fof anti-knife crime measures
OL,20,Fintroduced under Ronan's Law, named
OL,21,Fafter Ronan Kanda.
