OL,3,CNinja sword ban under Ronan's Law set
OL,4,Cto come into force by summer
OL,6,FAnyone caught with a ninja sword in
OL,7,Fprivate could face six months in
OL,8,Fprison, set to increase to two years
OL,9,Funder plans in the Crime and Policing
OL,10,FBill.
OL,12,FRonan's mother, Pooja said: "Today
OL,13,Fmarks a very important day for us as a
OL,14,Ffamily and our campaign.
OL,16,F"Since losing our beautiful boy Ronan,
OL,17,Fwe have relentlessly campaigned for a
OL,18,Fban on ninja swords ` the lethal
OL,19,Fweapon which took his life.
