OL,3,CNinja sword ban under Ronan's Law set
OL,4,Cto come into force by summer
OL,6,F"We believe ninja swords have no place
OL,7,Fin our society other than to seriously
OL,8,Fharm and kill.
OL,10,F"Each step towards tackling knife
OL,11,Fcrime is a step towards getting
OL,12,Fjustice for our boy Ronan.
OL,14,FShe continued: "Ronan was coming home
OL,15,Fonly two doors away when two 16-year-
OL,16,Fold's mistook him for their intended
OL,17,Ftarget and came behind and stabbed
OL,18,Fonce in his abdomen from the side.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
