OL,3,CNinja sword ban under Ronan's Law set
OL,4,Cto come into force by summer
OL,6,F"They also stabbed him in his heart
OL,7,Fwhen he turned around and he did not
OL,8,Fstand a chance as they inserted a
OL,9,Ftwenty inch ninja sword.
OL,11,F"These things are still available,
OL,12,Fthey are still children carrying these
OL,13,Ftypes of weapons, it's painful to see
OL,14,Fthat our world is surrounded by these
OL,15,Fthings, I welcome everything that we
OL,16,Fcan get."
OL,18,FThe weapons can be handed over in
OL,19,Fknife-surrender bins or local police
OL,20,Fstations under a surrender scheme
OL,21,Frunning in July.
