OL,3,CNinja sword ban under Ronan's Law set
OL,4,Cto come into force by summer
OL,6,FNo ninja swords bought after Thursday
OL,7,Fwill be eligible for compensation as
OL,8,Fpart of efforts to stop exploitation
OL,9,Fof the scheme, the Home Office said.
OL,11,FUnder Ronan's Law, the Home Office has
OL,12,Falso announced a raft of measures
OL,13,Fincluding making retailers report bulk
OL,14,For suspicious sales to police, and
OL,15,Fincreasing the jail sentence for
OL,16,Fselling weapons to children, or
OL,17,Fillegal blades such as zombie knives,
OL,18,Fto two years.
