OL,6,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said: "We
OL,7,Fare acting with urgency to bring
OL,8,Fforward measures to prevent deadly
OL,9,Fweapons from getting into the wrong
OL,10,Fhands and will continue to do whatever
OL,11,Fis needed to prevent young people
OL,12,Fbeing killed on our streets as part of
OL,13,Four mission to halve knife crime over
OL,14,Fthe next decade."
