OL,6,FPatrick Green, chief executive of Ben
OL,7,FKinsella Trust, also backed the ban,
OL,8,Fadding: "These weapons, with no
OL,9,Fpractical purpose beyond violence, are
OL,10,Fsimply instruments of war and have
OL,11,Fabsolutely no place in our society or
OL,12,Fon our streets."
OL,14,FThe Government is also set to consult
OL,15,Fon introducing a licensing scheme for
OL,16,Fretailers who want to sell knives in
OL,17,Fthe spring.
